Description:
You arrive at a small lake where some local werewolves are fishing, one of them approaches you and says:

"Hey, do you want to participate in our little fishing contest?  The entry fee is 60 gold and you will triple the gold if you win, the rules are very simple: 

We all compete and the group that gets the biggest fish wins. And of course cheating is not allowed."
